## keepassxc
for_window [class="(K|k)ee(P|p)ass(X|x)(C|c)"] floating enable, border normal, move to scratchpad, resize set 1000 650
no_focus [class="(K|k)ee(P|p)ass(X|x)(C|c)"]
bindsym $mod+o [class="(K|k)ee(P|p)ass(X|x)(C|c)"] scratchpad show
## doublecmd
for_window [class="(D|d)oublecmd" window_role="[^(TfrmMain)]{1}$"] floating enable, border normal
